83452nOJ75s9lQ8yBbvMa.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190222083453QKAi5lnsv9PVycYf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201902220834537RuNMEJ3TSAH6QWb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190222083453D9fI5YKGEvFezQHX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190222083454jg1zOG4dMYitxlVp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190222083454LyTQ9FKkuicIGV2B.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201902220834547LscpESAGz5gktFB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190222083456WdFiemQgVUIc8n1q.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/runway/fall-ready-to-wear-2019/milan/max-mara/review/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Max Mara 2019 秋冬：</a></strong></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190222083907PbxwmJo1V5urCTBK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201902220839063pJA7GKo5uH2WRbM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190222083905dFYAZzcq4TPKJkDs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190222083906MxEmPDJo6GV95FzU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190222083907qScaFTEuCin8eMs7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2019022208390729ptKMEqhCljfYyG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190222083908hp35CqxVWuTktGEX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190222083908bQYd52KpxDse140H.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190222083908zRNvaxPGeFZ46CKl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190222083909cxjNs0BMUnLbGZku.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190222083909qKHC0czMp5XgQrev.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201902220839102mb57On6hjBEV1ML.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190222083910D91GZne07VbAkQ4p.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190222083910mtEDO4WpN5uGnkwh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190222083910x1eZsIGHBT32X7im.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190222083911jicQ12DKPZUgGe7r.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190222083911sOeMnTFg1ywElU25.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190222083911mRZlPKcx17VhM8Ut.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201902220839116qFzATUHh52QNrJf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190222083911FMwX5RSK9va8DOLC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.vogue.co.uk/shows/autumn-winter-2019-ready-to-wear/moncler/collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">Moncler Genius 2019 秋冬：</a></strong></p><p>Moncler 与知名设计师合作的 Moncler Genius 项目进行到第三期。本期发布在意大利比萨市的&nbsp;Via Ferrante Aporti 街区举行，每位设计师占据一个空间做装置和展示，展期直至 2 月 24 日。</p><p>新加入的设计师包括英国新锐设计师 Richard Quinn，以及去年将品牌从 Alyx 改名 1017 Alyx 9SM 的创始人兼设计师 Matthew Williams。</p><p>此外还有往期已合作过的英国新锐设计师 Simona Rocha、Craig Green、日本潮牌 Fragment Design 创始人藤原浩、Valentino 创意总监 Pierpaolo Piccioli、Palm Angels 创始人&nbsp;Francesco Ragazzi、意大利高级宠物服装品牌 Poldo Dog Couture 以及手袋品牌 Valextra。</p><p>高端滑雪系列 Moncler Grenoble 将继续由&nbsp;Sandro Mandrino 设计，而原 Acne Studios 设计师 Sergio Zambon 和原 CELINE 设计师 Veronica Leoni 将分别负责 Moncler 1952 系列的男女装设计。</p><p>Moncler Genius 将分批发售，第一批预计将于今年 6 月上架。</p><p><strong>Moncler X Richard Quinn：</strong></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190222080000pTecKnhfPbiM8t6q.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2019022207595959uTz7mdsOGNUkrg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190222075959wXcGAgDoQvfY3riV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190222075959UnlQi80aDOmzq5v9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201902220800006ArVKIlyu74vhUtp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190222080000sh7r64vlI9eawMqg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><fig